Get a list of variant groups

getAllVariantGroups.Rd

Retrieve all variant groups from the CIViC DB

getAllVariantGroups(page = 1, count = 25)

Arguments

page

the page number to retrieve
count

the number of variant groups to retrieve

Value

An S3 Object of type civic_api containing the content, url, and response

Examples

getAllVariantGroups(count = 10)
